data.description: A must see move-in ready home located in Tolleson. Minutes from the Pecan Promenade shops, with walk trails and a community park just steps from your back door. Single-level home with an open spacious floor plan. Ample natural light, new appliances, granite countertops all within your open kitchen. This home is conveniently located in the Tivoli subdivision near Union Elementary school, and close to the i10 freeway. Welcome home!
